### Get all users
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users HTTP/1.1

### Get a single user
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/Leon1 HTTP/1.1

### Get a single user that doesn't exist
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/Joe HTTP/1.1

### Delete a single user
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/users/Bob1 HTTP/1.1

### Post a new user
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
"name": "Bob",
"username": "Bob1",
"password": "123"
}